imdb.plot outline: Personal trainer and actor, Pete Khoury could use a coach of his own. After going through another unexpected break up, Pete finally caves to jump into the pool of internet dating. As "Love Online" gets a new member, Pete's friends and 'LOL' pros Joe and Carl try to help Pete along the way...as does neighbor and "Love Online" editor, Kelly. Rosie (Kelly's hip mom), is also a veteran to "Love Online", which is where she hooks up with Larry. When Pete thinks about deleting his account on 'LOL', Kelly convinces him to give it more time and Carl pimps his profile. When Joe takes Pete to the race track, Joe bets the ponies as Pete thinks he found a winner behind the window. "Meet Pete" (aka, "Love Online"), will take you into the lives of four friends who are among millions trying to balance life, work and the endless challenges of internet dating. Find out if the rewards outweigh all of the trials and tribulations as Pete and his friends play the dating game...online!
